-D%E1%BB%8B/%E1%BB%A8c-Giang-Nam-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-hD9_tLjgioQp89heNZ0PtQ">Ức Giang Nam kỳ 1 - 憶江南其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br></div>	</div>
